        "action": "Mandate 24/7 real-time emergency monitoring on all social media platforms",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Legislate to require social media companies to implement 24/7 proactive emergency monitoring. This should include AI-driven detection of immediate threats\u2014such as severe cyber-bullying, self-harm, or illegal activity\u2014and a requirement to alert emergency services instantly when lives are at risk.",
